QuestData.Title: Deep Impact
QuestData.Description: Queen Azshara seeks entrance into the plane of water, for what I do not know.$b$bShe believes that the ancients held the keys to finding its location.$b$bI have personally been charged with scouring the ruins in this region, and none shall rest until we discover the secrets we seek!$b$bSubmerged just to the north are a concentration of ruins. Use this staff to search through the rubble.$b$bReturn to me only when you have located that which we seek!
QuestData.LogDescription: Priestess Valishj wants you to find the Ancient Engravings of Neptulon.
QuestData.RewardText: Yes! You've found it!$b$bNeptulon's engravings... there can be no mistake!
